Rocco was born in the dense forests on the outskirts of Solana.

Like any other raccoon, his days were filled with foraging and nights with scavenging.

However, Rocco was different; he possessed an uncanny intelligence and a curiosity that set him apart. While other raccoons were content with their simple lives, Rocco yearned for something greater.


He began by establishing connections with the city's underbelly, leveraging his small size and agility to gather intelligence and blackmail low-level crooks.


His cunning and ruthlessness quickly earned him a reputation.

As his wealth and influence grew, Rocco formed the "Night Claw Syndicate," a secretive organization that controlled Solana's black market, from illicit goods to underground gambling.

Where can I buy $ROCCO?

You have to Navigate to Dexscreener.com and click on the MoonShot tab, from there paste the Contract Adress of $ROCCO, connect your wallet in the right corner and click BUY.

What is MoonShot?

MoonShot is a fair launchpad created by Dexscreener, its a trustworthy platform where you can buy and trade memecoins, and raise liquidity in a trustful way.

What is Raydium?

Raydium is an automated market maker (AMM) built on the Solana blockchain which enables lightning-fast trades, permissionless pool creation, and new features for earning yield.

What is Raydium?

What happens when we raise our target on MoonShot?

MoonShot has a bonding curve contract that automatically migrates and locks the raised liquidity to Raydium, from there the token becomes available for millions of traders and the sky becomes our limit.
